Class wgResources

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<wgResource>
java.util.AbstractList<wgResource>
java.util.Vector<wgResource>
workloadgenerator.wgResources
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<wgResource>, Collection<wgResource>, List<wgResource>, RandomAccess, SequencedCollection<wgResource>
public class wgResources extends Vector<wgResource>
Represents a group of identical resources and metadata used by the workload generator (for example, a resource pool with a quantity).

The class extends Vector of wgResource and exposes helper methods to add resources, query counts and provide export header keys.

Author:
YC
